@{557058:490c665b-b69c-40f3-80ea-64f20747efc4} those spots were intended to be for metal cabinets, but only the collision blocks were placed. They have now been removed. Please download and install the new Docker images. For your local `catkin` workspace, remove your existing local models so the latest models are downloaded/installed.

`rm -rfv ~/.ignition/fuel/fuel.ignitionrobotics.org/openrobotics/models`
content.html:
@Martin Dlouhy those spots were intended to be for metal cabinets, but only the collision blocks were placed. They have now been removed. Please download and install the new Docker images. For your local catkin workspace, remove your existing local models so the latest models are downloaded/installed.

rm -rfv ~/.ignition/fuel/fuel.ignitionrobotics.org/openrobotics/models
